{"prompt": "Generate a website for a SaaS product. The website should be sleek and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>SaaS Product</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #007bff;\n            --secondary-color: #e0f0ff;\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --background-color: #ffffff;\n            --accent-color: #0056b3;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 90%;\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 40px 20px;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: white;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n        }\n\n        header p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            margin-top: 10px;\n        }\n\n        section {\n            padding: 60px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        #hero {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-color) 0%, var(--accent-color) 100%);\n            color: white;\n            padding: 80px 0;\n        }\n\n        #hero h2 {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        #hero p {\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: white;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;\n            border: 2px solid white;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: white;\n            border-color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        #features .feature-item {\n            display: inline-block;\n            width: 30%;\n            margin: 20px 1.5%;\n            padding: 30px 20px;\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            vertical-align: top;\n        }\n\n        #features .feature-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n        }\n\n        #features h3 {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            font-size: 1.6em;\n        }\n\n        #features p {\n            font-size: 1em;\n            color: #555;\n        }\n\n        #testimonials {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        #testimonials blockquote {\n            font-style: italic;\n            margin: 30px auto;\n            max-width: 700px;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            position: relative;\n            padding: 20px;\n            border-left: 5px solid var(--primary-color);\n            background-color: white;\n            border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        #testimonials cite {\n            display: block;\n            margin-top: 10px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--text-color);\n            color: white;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .container {\n                width: 95%;\n            }\n\n            #features .feature-item {\n                width: 90%;\n                margin: 20px 5%;\n            }\n\n            #hero h2 {\n                font-size: 2.5em;\n            }\n\n            #hero p {\n                font-size: 1.2em;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>InnovateX</h1>\n            <p>The Future of Productivity, Simplified.</p>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <section id=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Unlock Your Team's Potential</h2>\n            <p>Streamline workflows, boost collaboration, and achieve more with our intuitive SaaS solution.</p>\n            <a href=\"#pricing\" class=\"cta-button\">Get Started Today</a>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"features\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Key Features</h2>\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <h3>Seamless Integration</h3>\n                <p>Connect with your existing tools effortlessly. Our platform works with everything you use.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <h3>Intuitive Design</h3>\n                <p>A clean and user-friendly interface that requires no training. Get started in minutes.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <h3>Scalable Solutions</h3>\n                <p>Grow your business without limitations. Our platform scales with your needs.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"testimonials\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>What Our Clients Say</h2>\n            <blockquote>\n                \"InnovateX has completely transformed how our team operates. We're more efficient and collaborative than ever before!\"\n                <cite>- Jane Doe, CEO of Tech Solutions</cite>\n            </blockquote>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"pricing\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Simple & Transparent Pricing</h2>\n            <p>Choose the plan that best fits your business. No hidden fees, just powerful features.</p>\n            <div class=\"feature-item\" style=\"width: 45%; display: inline-block; margin: 20px 2.5%; background-color: var(--primary-color); color: white;\">\n                <h3>Pro Plan</h3>\n                <p style=\"color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);\">Ideal for growing teams.<br><span style=\"font-size: 1.8em; font-weight: bold;\">$49</span>/month</p>\n                <p>Includes all core features, priority support, and advanced analytics.</p>\n                <a href=\"#\" class=\"cta-button\" style=\"background-color: white; color: var(--primary-color);\">Sign Up for Pro</a>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-item\" style=\"width: 45%; display: inline-block; margin: 20px 2.5%; background-color: var(--accent-color); color: white;\">\n                <h3>Enterprise Plan</h3>\n                <p style=\"color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);\">For large organizations.<br><span style=\"font-size: 1.5em; font-weight: bold;\">Contact Us</span></p>\n                <p>Custom solutions, dedicated account manager, and enterprise-grade security.</p>\n                <a href=\"#\" class=\"cta-button\" style=\"background-color: var(--primary-color); color: white;\">Contact Sales</a>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 InnovateX. All rights reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Optional: Add any future JavaScript interactions here\n        console.log(\"SaaS Product Website Loaded\");\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}